{
  "text": "Limitations of the present study are its retrospective nature and the inclusion of patients admitted within a limited time frame, however many of the present studies are retrospective, and cohort number in this study is comparable to the number of similar studies from the literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . To make more clear-cut conclusions, prospective multi-centre studies with large-cohorts should be designed.",
  "correct_citation": {
